WEBVTT

00:00.300 --> 00:01.849
Now, Japan has unveiled plans...

00:01.984 --> 00:05.018
...for its biggest military build-up since World War II.

00:05.182 --> 00:07.875
The government says it will double defense spending,...

00:08.123 --> 00:12.609
...bringing it up to the NATO standard of 2% of GDP.

00:12.745 --> 00:16.564
Japan's move away from a self-defense only stance...

00:16.656 --> 00:19.261
...comes as it seeks to counter regional threats.

00:19.569 --> 00:23.590
It plans to acquire long-range missiles capable of striking China.

00:23.897 --> 00:28.297
Beijing said the plans undermine bilateral relations.

